Resource Profile: Clinical Study

Official URL: https://www.vision-zero-oncology.de/fhir/StructureDefinition/clinical-study Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2023-04-03 Computable Name: Clinical_Study

Copyright/Legal: CC-BY-SA-4.0

This profile describes a clinical study in which a patient takes part.

Usage:

  • Examples for this Resource Profile: ResearchStudy/ExampleStudyNapkonCovidom and ResearchStudy/ExampleStudyRAAINBOW

Description of Profiles, Differentials, Snapshots and how the different presentations work.
